The paper focuses on question answering using neural networks, which falls under the natural language processing (NLP) domain. Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of deep learning techniques, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also investigates the effect of transferring weights on model accuracy, which falls under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper deals with information retrieval and text classification, which falls under cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
